# odooLinux

A Linux system diagnostics tool with Odoo integration.

## Features

- Network diagnostics and testing
- System monitoring and reporting
- Battery status checking
- Disk usage analysis
- PDF report generation

## Installation

```bash
# Install system dependencies
sudo apt install python3-pip python3-venv wkhtmltopdf

# Install the package
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

```bash
# Show help
odoo-linux --help

# Network commands
odoo-linux network report  # Generate network report
odoo-linux network speedtest  # Run speed test
odoo-linux network ping google.com  # Ping a host
odoo-linux network wifi  # Get WiFi information

# System commands
odoo-linux system report  # Generate system report
odoo-linux system battery  # Check battery status
odoo-linux system disk  # Check disk usage
```

## Requirements

- Python 3.6 or higher
- Linux operating system
- wkhtmltopdf (for PDF report generation) 
